| `checkoutSuccess` | `/checkout/success` | `src/app/checkout/success/page.tsx` | Yes | Post-checkout confirmation page. Shows success message after Stripe redirects back with `?session_id=`. Refreshes cart context so floating basket updates. |
| `stripeConnectReturn` | `/stripe/connect/return` | `src/app/stripe/connect/return/page.tsx` | Yes | Stripe Connect onboarding return page. Checks verification status and shows success/pending message. |
